      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to rigorous standards to ensure both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. It offers a refined driving experience and a well-appointed cabin, representing an exceptional value for the discerning motorist. Our comprehensive inspection confirms its reliable performance and preserved condition, making it a premier choice for those seeking quality and longevity.",
      "price": 36800.0,
